This script acts as follows;
- search your favorite items in Amazon according to config file.
- write when the items will be in store on your Google calendar

1. You need Google account and Amazon web service account.

2. Prepare YAML config file
---------------------------------------------------------------
account: your_name@gmail.com
password: your_password
feed: http://www.google.com/calendar/feeds/something/private/full
aws-key: your_amazon_web_service_key
target:
  - actor: Brad Pitt
    category: DVD
  - title: LOST
    category: DVD
  - artist: Lady GAGA
    category: Music
  - author: David Heinemeier Hansson
    category: Books
  - title: Ruby
    category: Books
---------------------------------------------------------------

3. Run script
ruby1.9 amazon2gcal.rb your_config.yaml

